list.item:
•Treatment with LITFULO should not be initiated in patients with an absolute lymphocyte count (ALC) <500/mm3 or a platelet count <100,000/mm3 [see
Warnings and Precautions (5.7)
].

•Update immunizations according to current immunization guidelines [see 

   Warnings and Precautions (5.8)

].

text.paragraph:
ALC and platelet counts are recommended before treatment initiation and at 4 weeks after treatment initiation, and thereafter according to routine patient management [see 

                                    Warnings and Precautions (5.7)

                                 ].

list.item:
•Malignancy and Lymphoproliferative Disorders [see 

   Warnings and Precautions (5.3)

]

